  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Coordination and Supervision: </strong>Overseeing and coordinating Construction, Architectural, M&amp;E and ACMV works with other site activities, ensuring smooth workflow and minimizing delays.</li>\n  <li><strong>Technical Expertise: </strong>Interpreting technical designs and drawings, providing technical advice, and resolving technical issues on site.</li>\n  <li><strong>Quality Control: </strong>Monitoring the quality of project works, ensuring adherence to project specifications and standards.</li>\n  <li><strong>Safety Management: </strong>Ensuring that all site activities are conducted safely, implementing and enforcing safety procedures.</li>\n  <li><strong>Documentation and Reporting: </strong>Preparing progress reports, method statements, risk assessments, and other relevant documentation.</li>\n</ul>",
